title: 873. Broncos vs. Chargers Recap & Top 5 Most Rugged Running Backs Today
itunes:title: 873. Broncos vs. Chargers Recap & Top 5 Most Rugged Running Backs Today
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys break down the Monday Night Football game between the Broncos and Chargers. Then, the pair give their takes on Seahawks CB Tariq Woolen and Vikings WR Justin Jefferson and all the success both have been having this season. To wrap up the show, the guys discuss Bucky's list of the top 5 most rugged running back today.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
